   Chutney Cheese Pate


   From Chronicle files. A past winner of the weekly Favorite
Recipe contest.


   &QL;


   Ingredients: &QL; 
2 (3-ounce) packages cream cheese, softened &QL; 
1 cup (4 ounces) shredded sharp Cheddar cheese &QL; 
4 teaspoons dry cocktail sherry &QL; 
{ teaspoon curry powder &QL; 
 &QL; 
\ teaspoon salt (optional) &QL; 
1 (8-ounce) jar mango chutney, finely chopped &QL; 
1 or 2 green onions with tops, finely chopped &QL; 
Sesame or wheat crackers &QL; 
 &QL;


   Beat cream cheese with Cheddar, sherry, curry powder and salt.
(If using food processor, shred Cheddar first before combining with
other ingredients.) Spread mixture on serving platter, shaping a
layer about { inch thick. Chill until firm. At serving time, spread
chutney over top and sprinkle with chopped green onion. Spread on
crackers.


